arStrings.szText: It was a home, a headquarters, and a warehouse all in one for our little band of eccentrics, back in the day. The Pale Hand couldn’t afford anything nicer. The people who needed us most never had much coin to spend.
We called it the Den. Never would’ve guessed I’d find myself back here, where it all started.
But, whenever you need to hire our help, my friend, the mercenaries of the Pale Hand will be at your service.
